I thought it was a mistake by Ocean to make all their games from Navy SEALS onwards 128K only. I don't think a game like Pang for example really needed it, and it becomes a pain to load as a result. I never really got into their 1990s efforts because of that. The spectrum lost its 48K roots to an extent: no no no!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.ysrnry.co.uk/forums/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=70">Spector</a> — Thu Jul 07, 2011 12:16 am</p><hr />
